{"tid":1795231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警商場內刻意撞途人 江永祥辯稱「我睇直播就係互不讓路」","createTime":"2019-12-23T17:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T00:59:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e0020258d6de7a4553d69b14135f205d00f608c6","tid":1795231,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:28:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069495\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069495&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlphjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=30c893b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069495&h=a110681f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069495</a><br />\n<br />\n警商場內刻意撞途人 江永祥辯稱「我睇直播就係互不讓路」<br />\n<br />\n警商場內刻意撞途人  江永祥辯稱「我睇直播就係互不讓路」週一 2019-12-23 獨媒報導<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/files/styles/w775/public/column_images/2_167.jpg?itok=x6rkZEHc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fw775%2Fpublic%2Fcolumn_images%2F2_167.jpg%3Fitok%3Dx6rkZEHc&h=89c08b9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（獨媒特約報導）市民星期六到元朗形點商場內集會，有防暴警察刻意撞向一名男途人，並反指該途人撞向警察。警察下午舉行記者會，警察公共關係科高級警司江永祥稱，警方接報後到場，一男子在警掃蕩期間，迎面走向警方，「我睇直播就互不讓路，於是就引起碰撞。」他認為，只要雙方「講聲唔該借歪」便能解決。<br />\n<br />\n江永祥又稱，過往有太多類似的互不相讓情況發生，才有不理想的事情發生，呼籲多一分禮貌，少一分挑釁，「香港便會有真正的平安夜。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49262536308_b96f0805e1_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49262536308_b96f0805e1_z.jpg&h=62c5d229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n明晚為平安夜，警方明晚除了九龍公園徑外，不會在尖沙咀進行任何封路和安排警員在海邊站崗，只會在發生突發事件時才會封路和作特別交通安排。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/49262536498_abc4a12325_z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flive.staticflickr.com%2F65535%2F49262536498_abc4a12325_z.jpg&h=cfc39416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油尖警區副指揮官黃志威稱，不封路的安排為經風險評估，「請你相信警察，我哋呢班同事唔係第一年做平安夜更份。你拖男帶女享受、感恩呢個節日，定擺明出嚟搞事呢？請你相信我哋。我哋會分得到。」江永祥則稱，巿民佳節外出看燈飾，或是故意生事十分容易分辨，「故意生事嘅人用毫無理由嘅包裝到出嚟慶祝。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：周頌謙"},{"pid":"91ef0bcfe7ddae2c832ee2c774c065c933d1f175","tid":1795231,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:29:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">X&rsquo;MAS EVE 願平安歸香港🇭🇰</span><br />\n日期 : 12月24日 (二)<br />\n時間：19:00 - 22:00<br />\n地點：<br />\n元朗yoho<br />\n沙田 新城市<br />\n尖沙咀 海港城<br />\n旺角 朗豪坊<br />\n銅鑼灣 時代廣場<br />\nLink : @xmasevehkchannel"},{"pid":"39b25c84ba2d958783359495042fbe4b5697cbca","tid":1795231,"uid":53062,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:32:02.000Z","msg":"有晒片都講大話<br />\n難怪冇人信大埔唔係便衣開槍"},{"pid":"fe9323c73eca2a7768c186016b900aa4ad7bd5bb","tid":1795231,"uid":57221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"唔洗再post<br />\n已經有幾個post講過"},{"pid":"9730d64447f4db7237de3a5cf1cdec4576da237e","tid":1795231,"uid":168097,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:44:10.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人會睇呢個垃圾記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ced50035ea561af47784cfde4b106191bbf656a","tid":1795231,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:46:54.000Z","msg":"阿叻係咪跟佢學嘢"},{"pid":"e4fb1014cccd9e710e3187419b1545c051357452","tid":1795231,"uid":325716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:52:57.000Z","msg":"其實有咩情況要講唔該借歪呢<br />\n主要係怕撞到鬼嘅時候"},{"pid":"605ac869f37ac802b528626d23261c47df45d6e4","tid":1795231,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T17:55:35.000Z","msg":"合理"},{"pid":"abd7ea34764458d1faf7f873d72b320525043029","tid":1795231,"uid":43189,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T18:11:17.000Z","msg":"所以黃絲就係要學呢樣嘢<br />\n人不要面天下無敵<br />\n仲講道德潔癖？"},{"pid":"32d0c017770a4d3ef28382280237609e62f52c46","tid":1795231,"uid":7719